data.title: Murata Manufacturing Co., Ltd. Minato MIRAI Innovation Center
data.meta_description: Murata Manufacturing Co., Ltd. Minato MIRAI Innovation Center. Takasago Thermal Engineering will provide comprehensive system engineering centered on air conditioning for many years to come by utilizing advanced technology for the planning, design, construction, and maintenance of all kinds of buildings, factories, and facilities.
data.text: Features This facility leads marketing and new business creations, for automotive, IoT, energy, healthcare fields. Based on the concept of "a place to inspire future engineers," the public facility, "Mulabo!" is also opened to convey children the fun of science through electronics.
